{% extends 'Layout.twig' %}
{% block CONTENT %}

<div class="window">

    <h2>Form controls</h2>

    <p><strong>Dropdown</strong></p>
    {{ forms.ui_select('dropdown', {0 : 'Вариант 1', 1 : 'Вариант 2', 2 : 'Вариант 3'}, '1', 'placeholder="placeholder" data-search="true"') }}

    <p><strong>Inputs</strong></p>
    <p>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="input">
        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="disabled" disabled="true">
    </p>

    <p><strong>Group inputs</strong></p>

    <span class="group-control">
        {% spaceless %}
        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="item 1">
        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="item 2">
        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="item 3">
        {% endspaceless %}
    </span>

    <p><strong>Checked input</strong></p>
    <p>
        <label class="form-control"><input type="checkbox">Default</label>
        <label class="form-control"><input type="checkbox" checked="true">Checked</label>
        <label class="form-control"><input type="checkbox" disabled>Disabled</label>
    </p>

    <p><strong>Radio input</strong></p>
    <p>
        <label class="form-control"><input name="radio" type="radio">Default</label>
        <label class="form-control"><input name="radio" type="radio" checked="true">Selected</label>
        <label class="form-control"><input name="radio" type="radio" disabled="disabled">Disabled</label>
    </p>

    <p><strong>Button-o</strong></p>
    <p>
        <button type="button" class="form-control-o">Default</button>
        <button type="button" class="form-control-o form-control-o__default">Default color</button>
        <button type="button" class="form-control-o form-control-o__primary">Primary</button>
        <button type="button" class="form-control-o form-control-o__secondary">Secondary</button>
        <button type="button" class="form-control-o form-control-o__link">Link</button>
    </p>

    <p><strong>Button</strong></p>
    <p>
        <button type="button" class="form-control">Default</button>
        <button type="button" class="form-control form-control__default">Default color</button>
        <button type="button" class="form-control form-control__primary">Primary</button>
        <button type="button" class="form-control form-control__secondary">Secondary</button>
        <button type="button" class="form-control form-control__link">Link</button>
    </p>

    <p><strong>Button disabled</strong></p>
    <p>
        <button type="button" class="form-control" disabled="disabled">Default</button>
        <button type="button" class="form-control form-control__default" disabled="disabled">Default color</button>
        <button type="button" class="form-control form-control__primary" disabled="disabled">Primary</button>
        <button type="button" class="form-control form-control__secondary" disabled="disabled">Secondary</button>
        <button type="button" class="form-control form-control__link" disabled="disabled">Link</button>
    </p>

    <hr>

    <h2>Links</h2>
    <p>
        <a href="javascript:void(0);">Links</a>
        <a href="javascript:void(0);" data-ajax="true">Links ajax</a>
        <a href="javascript:void(0);" data-modal="true">Open modal</a>
    </p>

    <hr>

    <h2>Typography</h2>
    <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla molestie varius sapien, nec egestas nulla sagittis sit amet. Pellentesque interdum felis urna, vel mattis massa scelerisque id. Mauris non elit tincidunt, pulvinar ipsum in, congue turpis. Mauris laoreet sollicitudin molestie. Phasellus quis elit tempus, pulvinar est quis, tristique odio. Nam quis leo turpis. Nulla condimentum nibh gravida augue pharetra, eu elementum orci condimentum.
